The paper discusses optimization techniques for sparse estimation methods, which are commonly used in machine learning and data analysis. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). The paper also covers applications in image processing (cs.CV) and signal processing (cs.SI), which are additional sub-categories that could be relevant.
